alerts.title: Green Warning For Thunderstorm In Belgium - Coastal Zone
Yellow Warning For Thunderstorm In Belgium - Coastal Zone
alerts.description: Thunderstorms are locally expected with: 10 to 30 l/m in 1 hour, or 20 to 40 l/m in 6 hours, or 25 to 50 l/m in 24 hours, possibly with local strong windgusts or hailstones of 1 to 2 cm. Be careful.
